profile:
We are a small local company, serving the Regina and surrounding area in Saskatchewan. We specialize at interior renovations and custom decks, however will take on just about any project. We believe there are NO small jobs...just small thinking by some companies, but at Renovating Regina we treat every project with the same high level of importance and quality of work. 
We don't focus on speed, but instead strive for the best quality at affordable rates. The saying "You get what you pay for" is true, however it doesn't have to break the bank. 
This company started because of covid, however we have been doing this type of work for years. If you check out our reviews you'll see how happy our customers are with our work, so contact us today for a free estimate.
services: Electrical, Plumbing, Carpentry, Framing, Drywall, and Flooring just to name a few.
